Maaty Modifications
-------------------

* asgi_app.py
    Added defensive `_safe_tools_count()` and `_safe_tools_iter()` helpers
    that guard `mcp_server._tool_manager._tools` access against FastMCP
    private-API drift, preventing 500 responses on /health and /status
    when introspection fails. (This change is upstream-friendly and may be
    proposed as an upstream PR.)

* .github/workflows/docker-publish.yml
    Container image publishing workflow that builds linux/amd64 +
    linux/arm64 images on every push to main and on `maaty-v*` tags,
    publishing to `ghcr.io/memirutku/yargi-mcp-maaty`. This workflow is
    Maaty-deployment-specific and is not intended for upstream.


